WITH UserBadges AS (
    SELECT UserId, COUNT(*) AS TotalBadges
    FROM Badges
    GROUP BY UserId
),
TopUsers AS (
    SELECT U.Id, U.DisplayName, U.Reputation, UB.TotalBadges
    FROM Users U
    LEFT JOIN UserBadges UB ON U.Id = UB.UserId
    ORDER BY U.Reputation DESC, UB.TotalBadges DESC
    LIMIT 10
),
PostStatistics AS (
    SELECT P.OwnerUserId, COUNT(P.Id) AS TotalPosts, 
           SUM(CASE WHEN P.PostTypeId = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalQuestions,
           SUM(CASE WHEN P.PostTypeId = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalAnswers,
           SUM(P.ViewCount) AS TotalViews
    FROM Posts P
    GROUP BY P.OwnerUserId
),
UserPostStats AS (
    SELECT U.Id, U.DisplayName, PS.TotalPosts, PS.TotalQuestions, PS.TotalAnswers, PS.TotalViews
    FROM Users U
    JOIN PostStatistics PS ON U.Id = PS.OwnerUserId
    WHERE U.Id IN (SELECT Id FROM TopUsers)
)
SELECT U.DisplayName, U.Reputation, U.TotalBadges,
       UPS.TotalPosts, UPS.TotalQuestions, UPS.TotalAnswers, UPS.TotalViews
FROM UserBadges UB
JOIN UserPostStats UPS ON UB.UserId = UPS.Id
JOIN TopUsers U ON U.Id = UPS.Id
ORDER BY U.Reputation DESC

FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "ID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", "t"."TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t" ON "Users"."Id" = "t"."UserId"
ORDER BY "Users"."Reputation" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t"."TOTALBADGES" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t1") AS "t2"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "TOTALQUESTIONS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "TOTALANSWERS", SUM("ViewCount") AS "TOTALVIEWS"
FROM "Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId") AS "t4" INNER JOIN "Users" AS "Users0" ON "t4"."OWNERUSERID" = "Users0"."Id") ON "t2"."ID" = "Users0"."Id"

SELECT COALESCE("t12"."DISPLAYNAME", "t12"."DISPLAYNAME") AS "DISPLAYNAME", "t12"."REPUTATION", "t12"."TOTALBADGES", "t12"."TOTALPOSTS", "t12"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "t12"."TOTALANSWERS", "t12"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "t9"."DISPLAYNAME", "t9"."REPUTATION", "t9"."TOTALBADGES", "s1"."TOTALPOSTS", "s1"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "s1"."TOTALANSWERS", "s1"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "Users1"."Id" AS "ID", "Users1"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users1"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", "t7"."TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Users" AS "Users1"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t7" ON "Users1"."Id" = "t7"."UserId"
ORDER BY "Users1"."Reputation" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t7"."TOTALBADGES" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t9"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t10" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t10"."UserId" = "s1"."ID") ON "t9"."ID" = "s1"."ID"
ORDER BY "t9"."REPUTATION" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t12"

SELECT COALESCE("t0"."OWNERUSERID", "t0"."OWNERUSERID") AS "OWNERUSERID", "t0"."TOTALPOSTS", "t0"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "t0"."TOTALANSWERS", "t0"."TOTALVIEWS", "Users"."Id", "Users"."Reputation", "Users"."CreationDate", "Users"."DisplayName", "Users"."LastAccessDate", "Users"."WebsiteUrl", "Users"."Location", "Users"."AboutMe", "Users"."Views", "Users"."UpVotes", "Users"."DownVotes", "Users"."ProfileImageUrl", "Users"."AccountId"
FROM (SELECT "OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "TOTALQUESTIONS", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "TOTALANSWERS", SUM("ViewCount") AS "TOTALVIEWS"
FROM "Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId") AS "t0"
INNER JOIN "Users" ON "t0"."OWNERUSERID" = "Users"."Id"

SELECT COALESCE("t12"."DISPLAYNAME", "t12"."DISPLAYNAME") AS "DISPLAYNAME", "t12"."REPUTATION", "t12"."TOTALBADGES", "t12"."TOTALPOSTS", "t12"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "t12"."TOTALANSWERS", "t12"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "t4"."DISPLAYNAME", "t4"."REPUTATION", "t4"."TOTALBADGES", "t10"."TOTALPOSTS", "t10"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "t10"."TOTALANSWERS", "t10"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "Users0"."Id" AS "ID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users0"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", "t2"."TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t2" ON "Users0"."Id" = "t2"."UserId"
ORDER BY "Users0"."Reputation" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t2"."TOTALBADGES" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t4"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t5" INNER JOIN (SELECT "s1"."Id" AS "ID", "s1"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "s1"."TOTALPOSTS", "s1"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "s1"."TOTALANSWERS", "s1"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "t8"."ID"
FROM (SELECT "Users1"."Id" AS "ID", "Users1"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users1"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", "t6"."TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Users" AS "Users1"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t6" ON "Users1"."Id" = "t6"."UserId"
ORDER BY "Users1"."Reputation" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t6"."TOTALBADGES" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t8") AS "t9"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t9"."ID" = "s1"."Id") AS "t10" ON "t5"."UserId" = "t10"."ID") ON "t4"."ID" = "t10"."ID"
ORDER BY "t4"."REPUTATION" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t12"

SELECT COALESCE("OwnerUserId", "OwnerUserId") AS "OWNERUSERID", CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_1", CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_2", "ViewCount"

SELECT COALESCE("t12"."DISPLAYNAME", "t12"."DISPLAYNAME") AS "DISPLAYNAME", "t12"."REPUTATION", "t12"."TOTALBADGES", "t12"."TOTALPOSTS", "t12"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "t12"."TOTALANSWERS", "t12"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "t3"."DISPLAYNAME", "t3"."REPUTATION", "t3"."TOTALBADGES", "t10"."TOTALPOSTS", "t10"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "t10"."TOTALANSWERS", "t10"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "ID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", "t1"."TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t1" ON "Users"."Id" = "t1"."UserId"
ORDER BY "Users"."Reputation" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t1"."TOTALBADGES" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t3"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t4" INNER JOIN (SELECT "Users1"."Id" AS "ID", "Users1"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "t9"."TOTALPOSTS", "t9"."TOTALQUESTIONS", "t9"."TOTALANSWERS", "t9"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "t7"."ID"
FROM (SELECT "Users0"."Id" AS "ID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users0"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", "t5"."TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALBADGES"
FROM "Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t5" ON "Users0"."Id" = "t5"."UserId"
ORDER BY "Users0"."Reputation" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t5"."TOTALBADGES" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t7") AS "t8"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", SUM("FD_COL_1") AS "TOTALQUESTIONS", SUM("FD_COL_2") AS "TOTALANSWERS", SUM("ViewCount") AS "TOTALVIEWS"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "OWNERUSERID") AS "t9" INNER JOIN "Users" AS "Users1" ON "t9"."OWNERUSERID" = "Users1"."Id") ON "t8"."ID" = "Users1"."Id") AS "t10" ON "t4"."UserId" = "t10"."ID") ON "t3"."ID" = "t10"."ID"
ORDER BY "t3"."REPUTATION" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t12"
